Elastic Search
==============

This plugin is still in heavy development: do not use in production!


Development setup
-----------------

On your VM, install the elasticsearch PHP client:

    $ mkdir -p /usr/local/share/php
    $ cd /usr/local/share/php
    $ git clone git://github.com/nervetattoo/elasticsearch.git

Then, install elasticsearch:

    $ cd /opt
    $ wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/downloads/elasticsearch/elasticsearch/elasticsearch-0.19.0.tar.gz
    $ tar zxf elasticsearch-0.19.0.tar.gz
    $ cd elasticsearch-0.19.0

Start the server in background, to keep using your session:

    $ ./bin/elasticsearch

Or in foreground, to get logs:

    $ ./bin/elasticsearch -f
